INSERT INTO `mq_article` VALUES ('49', '测试文章8', 'art_title_en', '1', 'art_keywords_en', '69', '\\uploads\\article\\20190306\\f51f9d0b4cca43f118afadbb031c1f6b.png', null, null, null, null, '在未来，百度也会将人工智能技术运用到商业化营销中，将百度的大数据、云计算、人工智能赋能企业，对您来说，在商业方面更期待与百度有哪些方面的合作？', 'art_description_en', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“制造业是现代工业的基石，随着信息技术、新能源、新材料等重要领域和前沿方向的革命性突破和交叉融合，正在引发新一轮产业变革。为了推进智能制造的发展，中国发布了《中国制造 2025》，全面推进制造强国战略。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2014年在江苏昆山，一家专注于机器人及控制系统核心技术开发应运而生，短短几年就在国内各大展会频频获奖，备受业内关注。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190307/1551940117106077.jpg\" title=\"微信图片_20181030165717.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20181030165717.jpg\" width=\"929\" height=\"346\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 27.2px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2018年7月AMTS &amp; AHTE</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 27.2px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">最佳展商奖</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 27.2px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190307/1551940118973809.jpg\" title=\"微信图片_20181030165801.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20181030165801.jpg\" width=\"934\" height=\"682\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.6px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2018年8月北京世界机器人大会</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.6px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">获得最佳人气产品奖</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.6px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 22.4px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">荣誉背后承载的是技术基底和匠心打造，更是团队协作和企业战略。9月末，我们走进艾派科技，与其总经理张易功展开对话，请他讲述艾派的工匠精神与民族工业的崛起。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190307/1551940118844627.jpg\" title=\"微信图片_20181030165807.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20181030165807.jpg\" width=\"910\" height=\"1255\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 22.4px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">作为技术出身的张易功，并不像理工科一般寡言少语，将其艾派的产品和技术，他自信满满侃侃而谈，不难看出，从业多年，智能机器人不仅是他引以为豪的工作更是他愿意付诸实现的职业理想。而艾派无疑是根植他职业理想的最佳土壤。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 22.4px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 169, 0); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">作风严谨</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 22.4px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">作为一家以研发为核心的智能制造企业，高大上、理工科、工程师，这些固有印象一直深入人心，而通过堪比机场安检的重重关卡进入艾派科技之后才真正领略到技术型公司的严谨。而刚刚经历过和“拜访者”身份的我们一样经历的本公司总经理张易功并没有位高者的架子，反而跟我们解释，“一家公司总要有点规矩”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 22.4px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190307/1551940118547450.jpg\" title=\"微信图片_20181030165811.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20181030165811.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 22.4px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 19.2px; text-align: center;\">进入实验室</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 19.2px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">前</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 19.2px; text-align: center;\">被“没收”的手机</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 169, 0); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 169, 0); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">态度亲和</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 22.4px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">本次的采访约在上午，见面时张易功刚刚结束一场内部会议，从会场板书不难看出这里经历了一次头脑风暴。而与我们交谈中的他未见疲色，反而亲力亲为地收拾了一下刚刚留下的“残局”。这样的领导态度很显然也备受员工的喜爱，而采访中他也透露，愿意放权给管理层，也希望“每个团队都能有自己的脾气”。</span><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190307/1551940118139379.jpg\" title=\"微信图片_20181030165815.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20181030165815.jpg\" width=\"918\" height=\"565\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 19.2px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">工作中的张易功</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 169, 0); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">别样浪漫</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">交流中谈到机器人与人类未来的畅想，他坦言未来无法预知，或许未来机器人会取代人类，或许人类的未来并不圆满，但是或许会有“会跟人对话的冰箱”、“会知道你需求的电视”，他还谈到“机器人瓦力”和电影中的情节，而没有记错的话这除了是一个科幻电影之外，也不乏浪漫的爱情。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; line-height: 1.6; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这样也不难想象，在他的领导下会有员工们把沉闷古板的机器调教成表情包这样的事情为什么会发生了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin