: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">更多的魅力请围观采访实录</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: center; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">以下是采访实录</span></strong></p><p><section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); line-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">艾派科技是一家智能制造产业为主体的公司，并且专攻“机器人+视觉”方面的研究，您是为什么会想到这个研究方向的？经过这几年的磨合，您认为这一方向对您的吸引点有变化吗？</span></strong></p></section></section><section><section></section></section></section></section></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; line-height: 1.6; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.5em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">艾派科技母公司- 江苏杰士德精密工业有限公司是做非标出身，为某国际手机品牌自动化的系统集成供应商，使用 “机器人+视觉”的比重很高，在非标自动化行业，“机器人+视觉”是关键的零部件。公司一直有感于3C行业自动化已经做了超过十年，有赖同仁胼手砥足的奋斗，母公司业务呈爆发性的成长，同仁生活也好了起来。我们刚做时，手机以前很大，功能不多; 现在越来越小，功能反更复杂了，客户的需求也越来越多、项目要求完成时间越来越短。然而，很多事情也没有改变，许多自动化设备也就是软硬件升级，功能扩展与延伸罢了，十年前和国外采购的许多关键零组件，至今仍是在和对方采买; 中国已经成为制造「大」国，成绩世界有目共睹，但我们却还不是制造「强」国，这也是为什么我们会耗费巨资投入机器人与视觉自主研发的初衷，这点从未改变。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p><section><section><br/></section></section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">我们都知道欧洲的制造业在全球首屈一指，尤其是瑞士、德国这样的制造强国有着悠久的历史经验和精湛的技术优势，您认为这些在中国进行制造业转型升级的过程中有哪些值得借鉴的经验?</span></strong></p></section></section></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.5em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">毋庸置疑值得借鉴，以下三点。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.5em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">第一最佩服的就是，德国有“统一标准”。标准的制定非常重要，例如：工业4.0这个词，就是德国先喊出来的，大家就会跟着往那个方向走; EtherCAT(以太网控制自动化技术)的标准由德国倍福自动化有限公司(Beckhoff)制定，大家就只能跟着它的标准走。&nbsp;而我们是「跟随者」，而非「标准制定者」。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.5em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">第二，“工匠精神”，重视品质。200年前的英国工业革命时期， “Made in Germany”也曾被英国视为是「模仿者、粗制滥造」而特地修定了《商标法》，限定英国进口的德国产品必须标明产地。但德国持续投入技职教育与研发，重视 “工匠精神”，至今“Made in Germany”已经成为品质的保证，德国的骄傲，德国的知名企业如西门子、大众等，也都是实实在在的做好产品，而非炒房和金融。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.5em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">第三，“严谨心态”，德国人做事出名的严谨精确，标准流程、验证测试资料数据可量、可靠、可复制，也是值得学习。因此，艾派科技在发展经营上，特别注重研发、教育培训与数据化的管理，和一般企业不同的是，虽然校企合作短期是不可能带来任何收入，但我们持续的在做，员工培训、团队建设活动，工匠精神的培养与APE理念教育，我们也是不吝于投入，只有当员工觉得自己公司好，真的骄傲，那才会做出杰出的产品。而在评判大家产出的部分，也是希望以数据说话，客观、精准。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.5em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p><section><section><br/></section></section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 22.4px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">同类型的国际知名的四大公司（ABB、库卡、发那科、安川）大多为汽车行业提供服务，而艾派科技则选择为3C行业提供服务，为什么会选择不同的方向，未来艾派还会以3C行业为主导吗？</span></strong></p></section></section></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.5px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">APE来源于3C，生于3C。中国的3C产业制造大国丰沛的产能，就是我们最好的土壤。艾派科技未来仍会以3C为主。四大家族的强大，也是起源于欧、日系汽车产业的崛起，因此他们核心的经验就在汽车产业，3C产业没我们熟悉，而艾派的核心优势在于3C产业，我们没有要成为别人，我们希望做好自己，企业经营应选择自己的优势，资源有限，也无法投入过多的产业，不然可能会 “样样通、样样松”; 要做精、做强，就是我们现在的主要方向。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; line-height: 1.6; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.5px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p><section><section><br/></section></section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 22.4px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">与国内外同类型企业相比，您认为艾派科技最大的核心竞争力是什么?</span></strong></p></section></section></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; line-height: 1.6; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 27.2px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">我们最大的核心的竞争力来自于应用与研发的双引擎：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 27.2px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;十年3C经验的强大的应用技术团队</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 27.2px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">和外企或四大相比：艾派技术应用团队拥有超过10年的3C产业自动化经验，客户亦为国际手机品牌，本地经验与国际水准要求并具。过去工业机器人以汽车产业为主，外企也多半相依汽车产业而生。艾派科技不同，我们为民族工业而生。中国集中了全球70%的3C产品产能，无疑在全球举足轻重。欧日的汽车产业带起了四大家族的荣景，我们相信中国的3C产业也将诞生属于中国自己的机器人品牌。机器人、运动控制、视觉与附件，都为中国制造而设计。至今几个知名品牌机器人品牌，研发设计都还在国外，所以多数是将适用于国外的设计，复制到国内销售;而艾派是真正在中国研发、为民族工业崛起而服务、设计，并藉由这个平台，让我们每一个公司同仁与合作伙伴，都与我们一起成长转型。我们企业的使命是清楚的，中国人有个很大的优势就是学得快、不怕累，政府中国制造2025的方向也很清晰，我们将跟随国家政策，为中国制造的转型升级，尽企业与个人的一份心力。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 27.2px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;核心技术自主研发</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 27.2px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">和本地企业相比：多数仅提供机器人本体产品，但机器人可能仅是自动化生产系统的一小部分而已，方案服务与视觉部分都需要找外包。一旦自动化方案有问题， “手眼不协调”，解决一个生产线问题需要多方协商。你可以想象，如果一个人，就算有强大的臂膀，但他的眼睛是依靠另一个人指引的，那该能有多大的问题？艾派提供 “手眼结合”的方案，机器手与视觉都是以匠心精神，自主研发（但并非封闭系统，维持兼容开放），能更有效率的为客户解决问题。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; line-height: 27.2px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; line-height: 1.6; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p><section><section><br/></section></section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 22.4px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">与德国提出的工业4.0有异曲同工之妙的是，2015年政府提出了中国制造2025，如今距离当时提出已经过去2年，您认为在这一战略提出之后对企业有什么影响？在您看来中国的制造业这两年是在往那几个方向发展？在自动化、数码化、人工智能化这几个大方向上您更看好哪个方向？</span></strong></p></section></section></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; line-height: 1.6; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.5px;\">我们看到目前现况是：”中国制造2025”除了长江三角较往此方向靠，其他地区发展还没有到那样的程度，这也是市场相当大的潜力所在。 “中国制造2025”的政策吸引，无疑给许多企业诱因投入这个产业，这两年投入机器人产业的企业很多，我们也相信未来可能会有一波淘汰，唯有真的有实力的企业才能够留下。在自动化、数码化与人工智能这几个大方向上，我最看好人工智能，也是艾派科技要走的方向。</span></span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; line-height: 1.6; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.5px;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; line-height: 1.6; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p><section><section><br/></section></section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 22.4px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在企业发展过程的各个阶段总会面临不同问题，但是品牌和口碑可以说是一家成功企业的终极追求，在艾派科技发展过程中是怎样建立品牌和打造口碑的？有哪些方面的举措？</span></strong></p></section></section></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 22.4px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">艾派科技最重要的措施就是提供「保姆式服务」，为客户解决问题。品牌和口碑的建立一定来自于两个基础，产品服务是1，而宣传是后面的0，唯有产品服务做好了，为客户解决问题了，那么加成出来的品牌口碑效益就会是100、10,000、1,000,000以上的成长。另外，由于工业领域国内品牌建设的案例较少，我们会广泛学习国内外的成功经验、定期国际交流参访，尝试不同的品牌建设、营销工具，包含展会、百度关键字、信息流、AR与VR、仿真演示等等，只要道理说得通，都愿意尝试，并且要求数据化检验分析效果，一次次都要更进步、要小步快跑、快速迭代，我们不会是第二个ABB或KUKA，艾派科技会是自己的样子，找出最适合属于艾派科技的品牌路。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; line-height: 1.6; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 22.4px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p><section><section><br/></section></section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); line-height: 2; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); line-height: 2; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在未来，百度也会将人工智能技术运用到商业化营销中，将百度的大数据、云计算、人工智能赋能企业，对您来说，在商业方面更期待与百度有哪些方面的合作？</span></strong></p></section></section></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; line-height: 1.6; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.5px;\">商业方面更希望与百度有人工智能方面的相关合作，百度强大的大数据、云计算、人工智能，希望可为艾派提供更好的 “脑力赋能”。艾派科技(APE Technology)的英文名APE，就是 “猿人”的意思，因为猿人演化如同机器人，最接近人类但无法超越人。我们致力于发展 “手、眼、脚、脑” 的机器人生态体系，才有了现在工业机械臂与视觉软件的推出。目前立即能开始的常规搜索关键字、信息流等成效还在尝试，希望能做到有客户在江浙户一带搜索 SCARA、点胶、工业机器人等相关需求，就能够自动通知我们。我们今年与百度尝试合作AR，由于百度事业规模大，我们也还不够了解，艾派也希望未来有更多创意的交流与呈现，我们也愿意针对工业自动化领域提供我们的经验反馈、数据和应用场景。更期待，能够透过百度的大数据，了解客户的需求与市场趋势方向，提供客户感兴趣的趋势方向、人群个性喜好、自动化问题，作为艾派产品研发、服务改善的参考。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; line-height: 1.6; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; line-height: 1.6; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p><section><section>张易功个人履历</section><section><br/></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); line-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2003-2005 富士康科技集团NWInG电控工程师</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); line-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2005-2007 上海美商莫仕(Molex)电控软件师</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); line-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2007-2009 美商罗克韦尔自动化有限公司(Rockwell) 应用工程师 (AE)</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); line-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2009-今 江苏杰士德精密工业有限公司的第一位工程师，创业维艰，一路担任多种角色，从PM、机构、软件调试、客户沟通等，', 'art_content_en', '0', '1', '0', '1551866569', '1551940141', null, '0', '1551927144', '1', '0');
